v1.1.1 - small balance changes

New Content:
+ New Index Tiers

Changes:
+ Added more descriptive description to then 'Obelisk' furnace. [X]
+ Adds an 'Enchants Offline' subheader within the Enchanter.
+ Made crystal comets despawn after 5 minutes.
+ Added a few new admin commands. [X]
+ Added build credits for each item [X]
+ Add a global giveitem admin command, and confirmation when sent. Use ProfileStore messagehandler to handle this.
+ $/min and $/sec are now under ore limit
+ Items that you can only obtain once will complete all index entries underneath their tier (example: shiny mvp completes mvp, shiny mythic rebirth complete all rebirth entries)
