Bug Fixes:
+ Helio-grader conveyor now moves ore. [X]
+ Hoarded Treasure weird hitbox fix [X]
+ Crystal Comets now despawn after 5 minutes.
+ Enchanter no longer says "no refunds" when cancelling.
+ Multiple secrets of the same type can now appear in the Enchanter
+ Updated description of the Candy Bomb to reflect longer ore lifetime
+ People that do not own the Rebirth IV badge (and are rebirth 4+) have been awarded it. [X]
+ Crystal Comets are now crystal shaped (not crate shaped), and float up and down.

Balance Changes:
+ Ore Shrinker now shrinks ore by 15%, as opposed to the original 2.5%. [X]
+ Obelisk Furnace no longer looks for 'Red' ore, and now looks for 'Neon' ore. [X]
+ Alien Crate now costs 1Sp, as opposed to 50Sp. [X]
